* The Application

ToDo App

** ToDo details:
- Description
- Date (not required)
- Priorities (low, medium, high - default is low)

* Tech Details (Windows 7 64 bit)
- Node.js
- Express framework
- Frontend: jade
- Testing: Expresso
- Storage: MongoDB, Mongoose

** MongoDB install on Windows:
- Extract to C:\mongodb
- mkdir  C:\data\db
- Start: mongod.exe, shell is mongo.exe

** NPM packages
- *Run as normal user in the project directory*
npm install express jade less expresso nodemon connect-flash
npm install mongoose --mongodb:native
- Run module like node path\bin\module_name
- nodemon: no need to restart server, execute with nodemon app.js